creator: Freshly, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Food delivery that's nutritious and convenient in a weekly subscription delivery service. Freshly meals use only the freshest food and ingredients (never frozen), made by our team of chefs and nutritionists. Each meal is ready to eat in only 3 minutes—they’re fully cooked so all you have to do is heat ‘em up.

NUTRITIOUS FOOD DELIVERY
Freshly cooks nutritious and delicious food, delivered to your door on a weekly plan. From 4 meals up to 12 meals a week, Freshly is your app for tasty and nutritious food delivery.

DELIVERY FLEXIBILITY
Not at home for your food delivery? Easily update your delivery day in the app to select any day of the week! Change your meal plan food delivery to wherever you are, home, work, or school, you just need an address to start receiving incredible food delivery!

SAVING TIME
Take the stress out of meal prep, recipes, restaurants, reservations, take out, and cooking. Freshly delivers food that satisfies. No artificial sugars, healthy ingredients, gluten free, keto friendly, low carb, with plenty of options to delight everyone.

DESIGNED TO FIT YOUR LIFESTYLE
Our meals are crafted by our team of nutritionists and chefs to be nutritious and delicious. With Freshly meals, you get to say no to artificial ingredients, preservatives, gluten, and refined sugars. Our food can meet your needs for various diets including gluten free, keto friendly, low carb, high protein, and other lifestyles.

CUSTOMER SERVICE
Our customer service team is available 24/7 around the clock to help you pick out meals, learn details about your food delivery, assist with any delivery issue, or any other questions you have. Chat directly from the app or place a phone call, we're always here to help.


Now you can manage everything related to your Freshly subscription right in the app and start receiving deliveries today!

• Update your upcoming delivery, or skip a week in seconds.
• Track your food delivery in one tap, so you know when to expect your delicious and tasty meals at your door.
• Quickly change your delivery address in a dash!
• Browse delicious meals, customize your order, and see what’s new.
• Dig into everything you need to know about a meal—ingredients, nutrition, and what makes your food tasty.
• Set your dietary preferences.
• Quickly contact our customer care team via live chat, email, or phone.

About Freshly:

We started Freshly because we believe eating fresh, nutritious food every day should be easy for everyone. So we do all the hard work for you—sourcing high-quality ingredients, making sure each meal you eat is nutrient dense and packed with the good stuff, and expertly cooking your food to order so it tastes fresh and delicious.

No shopping, chopping, cleanup, recipes, meal prep, or worrying about what’s for dinner. And with Freshly meals, you get to say no to artificial ingredients, preservatives, gluten, and refined sugars.

Freshly meals use only the freshest food and ingredients (never frozen), made by our team of chefs and nutritionists. Each meal is ready to eat in only 3 minutes—they’re fully cooked so all you have to do is heat ‘em up.

NUTRITIOUS FOOD DELIVERY
Freshly cooks nutritious and delicious food, delivered to your door on a weekly plan. From 4 meals up to 12 meals a week, Freshly is your app for tasty and nutritious food delivery.

DELIVERY FLEXIBILITY
Not at home for your food delivery? Easily update your delivery day in the app to select any day of the week! Change your meal plan food delivery to wherever you are, home, work, or school, you just need an address to start receiving incredible food delivery!

SAVING TIME
Take the stress out of meal prep, recipes, restaurants, reservations, take out, and cooking. Freshly delivers food that satisfies. No artificial sugars, healthy ingredients, gluten free, keto friendly, low carb, with plenty of options to delight everyone.

DESIGNED TO FIT YOUR LIFESTYLE
Our meals are crafted by our team of nutritionists and chefs to be nutritious and delicious. With Freshly meals, you get to say no to artificial ingredients, preservatives, gluten, and refined sugars. Our food can meet your needs for various diets including gluten free, keto friendly, low carb, high protein, and other lifestyles.

CUSTOMER SERVICE
Our customer service team is available 24/7 around the clock to help you pick out meals, learn details about your food delivery, assist with any delivery issue, or any other questions you have. Chat directly from the app or place a phone call, we're always here to help.


Now you can manage everything related to your Freshly subscription right in the app and start receiving deliveries today!

• Update your upcoming delivery, or skip a week in seconds.
• Track your food delivery in one tap, so you know when to expect your delicious and tasty meals at your door.
• Quickly change your delivery address in a dash!
• Browse delicious meals, customize your order, and see what’s new.
• Dig into everything you need to know about a meal—ingredients, nutrition, and what makes your food tasty.
• Set your dietary preferences.
• Quickly contact our customer care team via live chat, email, or phone.

We started Freshly because we believe eating fresh, nutritious food every day should be easy for everyone. So we do all the hard work for you—sourcing high-quality ingredients, making sure each meal you eat is nutrient dense and packed with the good stuff, and expertly cooking your food to order so it tastes fresh and delicious.

No shopping, chopping, cleanup, recipes, meal prep, or worrying about what’s for dinner. And with Freshly meals, you get to say no to artificial ingredients, preservatives, gluten, and refined sugars.
